    "name": "Mesh Independence Study — VAD CFD Domain",
    "description": "Systematic refinement of the CFD mesh across three resolution levels (coarse, medium, fine) for the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under VAD operating conditions. Grid convergence index (GCI) computed for velocity and shear-stress fields at the impeller outlet. Activity conducted to satisfy discretization error credibility factor requirements at MRL 5.",
    "activityType": "GridConvergenceStudy"
